ZH: 这片土地已经被开垦成了一片农田。
EN: This land has been cleared for farming.

ZH: 农民们为了开垦这片土地付出了很多努力。
EN: Farmers put in a lot of effort to clear this land for cultivation.

ZH: 他们打算开垦山谷上的土地，种植水稻。
EN: They plan to clear the land on the valley and plant rice.

ZH: 开垦荒地是一个漫长而辛苦的过程。
EN: Reclaiming wasteland is a long and arduous process.

ZH: 在这个地区，不断地开垦土地使得环境恶化。
EN: Continuous land clearing in this area has degraded the environment.

ZH: 河流两岸的地区正在被开垦成为新的城市。
EN: The areas along the river are being reclaimed for new urban development.

ZH: 许多农场主都会进行大规模的开垦土地以扩大农田。
EN: Many farmers will clear large areas of land to expand their fields.

ZH: 开垦过程中，我们发现了许多珍贵的植物种类。
EN: During the clearing process, we discovered many rare plant species.

ZH: 开垦森林地区会导致生态平衡的破坏。
EN: Clearing forested areas can disrupt the ecological balance.

ZH: 这个国家正在进行广泛的开垦活动改善土地利用率。
EN: This country is engaging in extensive land reclamation to improve land utilization rate.

ZH: 开垦过程中要注意保护土壤资源，避免土壤侵蚀。
EN: During land clearing, attention must be paid to soil conservation to prevent erosion.

ZH: 农民们需要使用合适的方法来开垦土地，保持土地肥沃。
EN: Farmers need to use appropriate methods to clear land and keep the soil fertile.

ZH: 政府计划开垦旱地以建设更多的水利设施。
EN: The government plans to reclaim dry land to build more water facilities.

ZH: 这片土地正在被开垦为一个新的城市公园。
EN: This land is being developed into a new city park.

ZH: 开垦这片荒地为旅游景点将为当地带来很大的经济利益。
EN: Developing this wasteland into a tourist attraction will bring significant economic benefits to the area.

ZH: 这个项目旨在开垦沼泽地以种植特殊的水生植物。
EN: This project aims to reclaim marshland for the cultivation of special aquatic plants.

ZH: 部分土地因为被过度开垦而出现了土壤退化问题。
EN: Some lands are suffering from soil degradation due to excessive clearing.

ZH: 开垦活动对当地的生态系统产生了不良影响。
EN: Land reclamation activities have had negative impacts on the local ecosystem.

ZH: 农民们正努力开垦新的耕地以满足市场需求。
EN: Farmers are working hard to reclaim new arable land to meet market demand.

ZH: 这块土地的开垦将为当地村庄带来新的经济机遇。
EN: The development of this land will bring new economic opportunities to the local village.
